l Morrissey 配音）的建筑工程师，他热情正直，善良可亲，其出色的建筑本领更是为镇上的人们所称道。巴布和温蒂共同经营者建筑王国，他们有很多得力的助手：红色推土机马克、黄色推土/挖土机耍酷、吊车小芙、压路机罗利、搅拌机狄丝，这些小伙伴在巴布的带领下共同建设着这座美好的城市，并且在这一过程中，也发生着各种各样有趣的事情。他们的口号是：“我们行不行？（Can We Fix It?）”“我们一定行！（Yes, We Can!）”（简介中人名翻译遵照台版）。\r\n\r\n本片为英国BBC电视台于1999年开播的系列动画，已在世界上140多个国家播出。","name":"Bob the Builder","name_cn":"巴布工程师","tags":[{"name":"欧美","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"英国","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"子供向","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1998","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1990-1999","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"KeithChapman","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"英国动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1999","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日常","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"巴布工程师"},{"key":"话数","value":"331"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"1998年11月28日"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"BBC (UK); Nick Jr. (US, 2001–2005); PBS Kids (US, 2005–present); Channel 5 (UK, 2015–present); Rai YoYo"},{"key":"导演","value":"Steven Feldman, Fred Holmes, Brian Mack, Liz Whitaker (Ep 1); Sarah Ball; Brian Little"},{"key":"音乐","value":"Paul K. Joyce"},{"key":"原作","value":"Keith Chapman"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":20,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":5,"7":12,"8":0,"9":1,"10":1},"score":6.9},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":2,"dropped":6,"wish":4,"collect":30,"doing":0},"id":225423,"eps":331,"meta_tags":["TV","子供向","日常","欧美"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1998-11-27","platform":"OVA","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a4/5e/86528_o6SY5.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a4/5e/86528_o6SY5.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a4/5e/86528_o6SY5.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a4/5e/86528_o6SY5.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a4/5e/86528_o6SY5.jpg"},"summary":"1998年9月23日にケイエスエスより発売され